  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "INTERIOR DESIGNER",
  "description": "<p><strong>SHADES OF LIFE</strong> is a Singapore based multi-disciplinary design studio with own in house carpentry that practices spatial , furniture and product design.</p><p>With a vast experiences in hospitality , commercial and residential projects , SHADES OF LIFE is able to offer a wide spectrum of design proposals and solutions to our clientele.</p><p><strong>WHO WE WANT</strong></p><p>Seeking for that creative individual who is self motivational , responsible with a never-say-die attitude to be part of the fun dynamic design crew</p><p><strong>QUALIFICATIONS</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Interior Design.</li></ul><p><strong>PROFICIENCY</strong></p><ul><li>Proficient in CAD.</li><li>3DS MAX, VRAY CORONA RENDER, RHINO (bonus attributes)</li><li>Creative eye for details in conceptualisation , design and design presentation process.</li><li>Familiarity with all phrases of projects , potential issues and proven history to produce completed projects.</li><li>Problem solving skills and self starter.</li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY</strong></p><p>Interested applicants do send us your CV and recent portfolio , attached with a current photo of yourself to <strong>shadesoflife729@gmail.com</strong><br /><br /><strong>Priority SINGAPOREAN AND PR </strong></p>",
